## **Teach the Gold Standard of Concealed Carry**

As an NRA CCW Instructor, you will be authorized to teach students how to safely and effectively carry a concealed firearm for self-protection. This course goes beyond basic marksmanship, emphasizing the mindset and skills required for personal defense in the real world.

### **Prerequisites**

- Must be an NRA Certified Pistol Instructor.
- Must have completed the NRA CCW student course.
- Must pass the NRA CCW Instructor shooting qualification.
- Must demonstrate a high level of proficiency and safety.

If you have any questions, call [1-571-210-5651](tel:15712105651), or email at [class@livefireinstruction.com](mailto:class@livefireinstruction.com)
